STIMULI
___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________	
see section Editable Stimuli

___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________	
INSTRUCTIONS 
___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
see section Editable Instructions

___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________	
EDITABLE CODE 
___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________	
check below for (relatively) easily editable parameters, stimuli, instructions etc. 
Keep in mind that you can use this script as a template and therefore always "mess" with the entire code 
to further customize your experiment.

The parameters you can change are:

Responsekeys/Labels:
/keyred:							the red response button (default: 32 -> d)
/keygreen:							the green response button (default: 33 -> f)
/keyblue:							the blue response button (default: 36 -> j)
/keyyellow:							the yellow response button (default: 37 -> k)

/getReadyDuration:					the duration (in ms) of the get-ready-trial (default: 5000ms)
</usermanual>

