<%parameters.keyred%>   for red words
<%parameters.keygreen%>  for green words
<%parameters.keyblue%>  for blue words
<%parameters.keyyellow%>  for yellow words

as quickly and as accurately as possible.  
If you make a mistake, keep going."
/ 2 = "~nYou will see a series of words displayed in different colors.
Indicate the color of the word by pressing either of the following <%expressions.buttoninstruct1%>s:

<%parameters.keyred%>   for red words
<%parameters.keygreen%>  for green words
<%parameters.keyblue%>  for blue words
<%parameters.keyyellow%>  for yellow words

as quickly and as accurately as possible.  
If you make a mistake, keep going.~n
For example, when this word appears,~n~n~n
you would press the <%parameters.keyred%>-<%expressions.buttoninstruct1%> for ''red'' as quickly as possible."
/ 3 = "~nYou will see a series of words displayed in different colors.
Indicate the color of the word by pressing either of the following <%expressions.buttoninstruct1%>s:

<%parameters.keyred%>   for red words
<%parameters.keygreen%>  for green words
<%parameters.keyblue%>  for blue words
<%parameters.keyyellow%>  for yellow words

as quickly and as accurately as possible.  
If you make a mistake, keep going.~n
For example, when this word appears,~n~n~n
you would press the <%parameters.keyred%>-<%expressions.buttoninstruct1%> for ''red'' as quickly as possible.
~nFor example, when this word appears,~n~n~n
you would press the <%parameters.keyblue%>-<%expressions.buttoninstruct1%> for ''blue'' as quickly as possible.
~nLet's practice a few words before we begin."
/ 4 = "~n~n~n~n~n~n~n
When you are ready to begin the task, press the SPACE BAR."
</item>

