	values.stimworditemnumber: 	stores the itemnumber of the current stimword
	'values.condition':			contains a numeric representation of the current condition:
								1=congruent, 2=incongruent, 3=HPF, 4=NTF, 5=HPFA, 6=NTFA
								
								
